 this in EF and Permafrost I think.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica">Mercalius</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica">hehe<P>server-shard...whatever...<P>I still havent officially cancelled my UO account yet, so bear with me.<P></FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica">Kern the Hunter</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica">-It took me a while to drop my UO account as well. I wish I sold it via E-Bay.<BR>-As for that Polar cloak any White Polar Bear skin and 5PP will work the Hard part is finding him before he is killed. The two to three times I have seen him I didnt have my skins on me, and he was killed shortly after. They should give the GZ to Martar pump him up a little more and let him use it on the murderers, hehe as it is now he some sort of Barbarian Monk punching for 70+. Now, whenever I plan on going into Everfrost or Permafrost I take those skins with me. I want my Polar Bear Cloak dammit! Even though I probably wont use it much I just want to say I got one.<P>------------------<BR>On the Cazic Thule Server<BR>*Kernan Fenrirson Barbarian Warrior,25th Rank of the Wolves,Naked LongWalk Hating Weilder of the LangSeax.{Highpass Heavy Guards}"For Halas and Glory!"<BR>*Orkus Barbarian Shaman 16th Vision,Spirit Weilding DEMI-GOD in the making.<BR>*Ahirah Dwarven Paladin 9th Tier "Fear me Evil, for I weild the Rantho Rapier!" <P>-"Never argue with an Idiot. First they drag you down to thier level, then beat you with experience." -Unknown</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE></td></tr></table> 
